Screen 2 - Alarm List


This will list all the Alarms set by the user(upcoming should come on the top)
Alarms in off mode are distinguishable
For Alarms set for all days should show as Everyday, For Weekdays as Weekdays and for Weekend as weekends, and with specific day/s and label
Users should be able to set the alarm on/off from this list
Clicking on "Add" will let the users set a new Alarm

